In week seven's Associated Press Poll, Baylor moves ahead of fellow Big 12 competitor TCU for the No. 2 ranking in the country. WVU will see both these teams back-to-back starting at Baylor on Saturday. And as it's been all season, Ohio State remains the top-ranked team.
